PN,41501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FTwo amateur pollution detectives have
OL,8,Fpublished data that they say proves
OL,9,FThames Water has been dumping illegal
OL,10,Fsewage into rivers for years.
OL,12,FAshley Smith is a former senior police
OL,13,Fofficer, and Professor Peter Hammond
OL,14,Fan academic.
OL,16,FThey're both retired and are close
OL,17,Fneighbours, living next to the River
OL,18,FWindrush in North Oxfordshire. They've
OL,19,Fspent the past ten years trying to
OL,20,Flift the lid on what they call the
OL,21,Fscandal of Britain's polluted rivers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FThis week their campaign group
OL,8,FWindrush Against Sewage Pollution
OL,9,F(WASP) published a comprehensive
OL,10,Freport that says over the past five
OL,11,Fyears, almost a quarter of Thames
OL,12,FWater's sewage spills were illegal.
OL,14,FAnd the worst affected river according
OL,15,Fto their data is the River Pang.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FIt's a small chalk stream that winds
OL,8,Fthrough the West Berkshire countryside
OL,9,Ffrom its source in Compton to join the
OL,10,FThames at Pangbourne, and campaigners
OL,11,Fsay it is the most sewage polluted
OL,12,Friver in the Thames Water region.
OL,14,FWindrush Against Sewage Pollution
OL,15,Fcampaigner Ashley Smith says water
OL,16,Fmanagement should be taken away from
OL,17,Fprivate companies: "I thought maybe
OL,18,Fthe regulation would be legitimate,
OL,19,Fthat you'd be able to take the truth
OL,20,Fto power and something might happen,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"But we very quickly learned that
OL,8,Fwasn't the case.
OL,10,F"It has actually just been journalism,
OL,11,Fhonest journalism, and exposing the
OL,12,Ffacts to the public that have driven
OL,13,Fthis and made it possible for the
OL,14,Fpublic, possibly to be served as they
OL,15,Fshould be, responsibly and to protect
OL,16,Fpublic health and the health of our
OL,17,Fwaters.
OL,19,F"We want to see the public getting a
OL,20,Fchoice we don't see.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"We don't want all the choices to be
OL,8,Fmade by powerful business interests.
OL,10,F"It's what we're saying. You know, the
OL,11,Fgovernment is signing up with very
OL,12,Fpowerful business interests, serving
OL,13,Fthem, wanting to deregulate to make
OL,14,Flife easier for them.
OL,16,F"Well, that means making life worse
OL,17,Ffor the rest of us."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FCampaigner Peter Hammond says his
OL,8,Fbackground in science helped them
OL,9,Finterpret the mass of information they
OL,10,Fwere collecting.
OL,12,F"We're in a little hamlet, 28 people
OL,13,For so.
OL,15,F"We started focusing on looking at one
OL,16,Friver and then realising it was a more
OL,17,Fgeneric problem, and then we looked at
OL,18,Fthe sister rivers nearby.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Then when I started publishing data,
OL,8,Fpeople approached me from all around
OL,9,Fthe country and I started looking for
OL,10,Ftheir rivers and it gradually
OL,11,Fescalated.
OL,13,F"Like most people we started off just
OL,14,Flooking in the river, testing things,
OL,15,Fbut then realising, as my training as
OL,16,Fa scientist, I knew that to do that
OL,17,Fproperly you needed lots of data.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Lots of people testing the river, in
OL,8,Fall kinds of different places, all
OL,9,Fweathers, all year round, and then I
OL,10,Frealised I could get data from the
OL,11,Fwater companies.
OL,13,F"So it was their data that they
OL,14,Fcouldn't question it, and then I could
OL,15,Fanalyse it and see whether they were
OL,16,Factually doing the job they were
OL,17,Fsupposed to do."
OL,19,FThe focus of much of the anger is the
OL,20,FSewage Treatment Works at Hampstead
OL,21,FNorreys.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FThe WASP data shows that the River
OL,8,FPang chalk stream in West Berkshire is
OL,9,Fthe worst affected by illegal sewage
OL,10,Fspills in Thames Water's region.
OL,12,FThe data was released following WASP's
OL,13,Frole in the Channel 4 drama "Dirty
OL,14,FBusinesses".
OL,16,FThe series portrays a decade-long
OL,17,Finvestigation into sewage contaminated
OL,18,Fwater by Water Companies in
OL,19,FOxfordshire revealed by Smith and
OL,20,FHammond.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,FTheir report also highlights the
OL,8,Fplaces where river pollution is at its
OL,9,Fworst - and which parliamentary
OL,10,Fconstituencies they fall into. The
OL,11,Fauthors say they want MPs to know
OL,12,Fwhat's happening in their area and to
OL,13,Fdo something about it.
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrat MP for Newbury,
OL,16,FLee Dillon added: "The scale of
OL,17,Fillegal sewage discharges exposed
OL,18,Ftoday is nothing short of an
OL,19,Fenvironmental disaster on an
OL,20,Findustrial scale.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"The figures confirm what communities
OL,8,Fin Newbury have been living with for
OL,9,Fyears: a water system that is failing
OL,10,Fus, failing our rivers, and failing
OL,11,Fthe very ecosystems it is meant to
OL,12,Fprotect. Here in Newbury alone, we saw
OL,13,F24 days of illegal spills at our
OL,14,Fsewage works and more than 8,900 hours
OL,15,Fof sewage released into our rivers
OL,16,Flast year, a level of pollution no
OL,17,Fcommunity should ever have to tolerate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Our chalk streams, the Kennet and the
OL,8,FPang, are among the rarest freshwater
OL,9,Fhabitats on the planet, yet Thames
OL,10,FWater has treated them as if they are
OL,11,Fexpendable.
OL,13,F"These rivers are internationally
OL,14,Fsignificant, environmentally fragile,
OL,15,Fand deeply valued by our community,
OL,16,Fbut instead of safeguarding them,
OL,17,FThames Water has allowed repeated
OL,18,Fillegal discharges, deferred essential
OL,19,Fupgrades, and hidden behind unreliable
OL,20,Fand inconsistent data.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"This is the consequence of a broken
OL,8,Fmodel that prioritises complex
OL,9,Ffinancial structures over basic
OL,10,Fenvironmental responsibility. Enough
OL,11,Fis enough. We cannot keep asking
OL,12,Fbillpayers to shoulder the cost of
OL,13,Ffailure while our precious rivers pay
OL,14,Fthe ultimate price. That is why I am
OL,15,Fcalling for Thames Water to be placed
OL,16,Finto special administration, so we can
OL,17,Ffinally break the cycle of
OL,18,Funderinvestment, restore
OL,19,Faccountability, and put the health of
OL,20,Four rivers, and the rights of our
OL,21,Fresidents, ahead of offshore creditors
OL,22,Fand financial engineering.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"We deserve clean water, honest
OL,8,Freporting, and a water company that
OL,9,Fworks for people and the environment.
OL,10,FToday's findings make one thing
OL,11,Fabundantly clear: the time for excuses
OL,12,Fhas passed; the time for action is
OL,13,Fnow."
OL,15,FIn a statement, Thames Water said: "We
OL,16,Fare currently reviewing Professor
OL,17,FHammond's report and have not
OL,18,Fvalidated it, so we are unable to
OL,19,Fcomment on the stated conclusions.
OL,26,@uD@EO]wD@dOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Taking action to improve the health
OL,8,Fof our rivers remains a key focus for
OL,9,Fus and over the next five years we are
OL,10,Fdelivering the most significant
OL,11,Fupgrade to our wastewater network in
OL,12,F150 years. This includes increasing
OL,13,Ftreatment capacity, reducing storm
OL,14,Fdischarges and introducing new
OL,15,Fnutrient-reduction schemes.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Hampstead Norreys Sewage Treatment
OL,8,FWorks has been undergoing a #6.4
OL,9,Fmillion improvement programme since
OL,10,FMarch last year that is intended to
OL,11,Fstrengthen its operational resilience
OL,12,Fand support the consistent treatment
OL,13,Fof flows received at the works.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"Upgrades at Compton Sewage Treatment
OL,8,FWorks are scheduled to begin this
OL,9,FSpring that are also intended to
OL,10,Fstrengthen operational resilience and
OL,11,Fhelp ensure consistent treatment of
OL,12,Fflows at the works, supporting good
OL,13,Fpractice in managing treated effluent
OL,14,Fwithin the Pang catchment.
OL,16,F"We are always committed to seeing
OL,17,Fwaterways thrive, but we can't do it
OL,18,Falone. Farming, industry, road runoff,
OL,19,Fwildlife, and increasingly extreme
OL,20,Fweather also play a role in river
OL,21,Fhealth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772697873
OL,3,CIllegal sewage dumps reveal most
OL,4,Cpolluted river according to
OL,5,Cenvironmentalists
OL,7,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,8,Fthe Environment Agency and local
OL,9,Fpartners to understand where
OL,10,Fimprovements to our assets might be
OL,11,Ffurther required in future, so that
OL,12,Fcommunities can continue to enjoy
OL,13,Ftheir rivers."
OL,26,@uD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G18/18
